Name: Ultimate Waifu Battle Online
About the game: UWBO is a Tower-Defense Game about some cute waifus that try to prevent the invading monsters from absorbing the energy from the Energy-Crystals. What you can expect You shoot the monsters, build turrets and help each other to prevent the monsters from destroying the Energy-Crystals. You can select different maps to defend the world from the monster invasion. two gamemodes classic tower defense competetive defense mode to see which team can survive longer Are you ready to help vulnerable girls defend the world ?
